SECTION 3. Subject to available funding, on or before July 1, 2028, the department of
transportation shall complete the construction of, or have begun the construction of, at least one
(1) family restroom as described in Section 1 at a safety rest stop.
SECTION 4. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
